*Pomognem* mu da reši problem. (I will help him to solve the problem.)

Moj tim je spreman da *pomogne* svim članovima. (My team is ready to help all the members.)

Ona nije mogla da *pomogne* nikome. (She couldn't help anyone.)

Oni su se složili da *pomognu* u potrazi. (They agreed to help in the search.)

Ona je odlučila da *pomogne* ljudima. (She decided to help people.)

Želim da *pomognem* u obnovi grada. (I want to help with the rebuilding of the city.)